{{#*inline "content"}}
<p>Thank you for joining our community. Your registration has been successfully processed and you're now part of our developer community.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <div class="info-row">
    <div class="info-label">Member</div>
    <div class="info-value">{{name}}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <div class="info-label">Communities</div>
    <div class="info-value">
      <span class="communities-list">{{communities}}</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <div class="info-label">Registration Date</div>
    <div class="info-value">{{date}}</div>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <div class="info-label">Status</div>
    <div class="info-value">Active</div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>At Shinobi Open-Source Academy, we focus on practical learning through real-world projects and peer collaboration. Our communities provide structured learning paths, mentorship opportunities, and hands-on experience with modern development practices.</p>

<p><strong>What to expect:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Weekly community meetings and technical discussions</li>
  <li>Project collaboration opportunities with other developers</li>
  <li>Access to learning resources and documentation</li>
  <li>Mentorship from experienced developers in your chosen communities</li>
  <li>Networking opportunities with like-minded professionals</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Important:</strong> You'll receive community meeting invitations and general updates every Monday. Please ensure your email notifications are enabled to stay informed about upcoming events and opportunities.</p>
{{/inline}}